    {
      "para_id": "Q000986.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Inana , the lady of battle , his beloved spouse , Amar-Suena , whose name was proclaimed by Enlil in Nibru , the steadfast supporter of Enlil's temple , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , fashioned her bronze ... of the E-ĝipar . He dedicated it to her for his well-being ."
    }
  ],
